snippet.textDisplay:
Bhai ne gaane ke pehle 10 second mein hi sab set kar diya 🔥🔥 Yo na sirf gaana hai, ye toh Haryane ki dhadkan hai! Desi beat, asli awaaz, aur attitude full 100 — iska vibe seedha dil mein jaaga se 💯
Jitne bhi singers aaj kal trend mein hain, sab ne side le li is OG artist ke saamne! Haryana ka original swag fir se zinda kar diya bhai ne 🐂🎶 Jaatland se leke Delhi tak sabhi ne repeat pe daal diya hoga ye track 🚜🔥
